The paper presents a new implementation of a data structure, specifically a non-blocking doubly-linked list, for an asynchronous shared-memory system. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Operating Systems (cs.OS), Programming Languages (cs.PL), and/or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
